#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:56
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Academic record is requested to enable analysis of the effect of "
"qualifications on research performance,\n"
"        career trajectories, and to better understand needs for succession "
"planning and support for particular groups.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"E tonoa ana he whakaaturanga mātauranga kia taea ai te tātari te pānga o ngā "
"tohu ki te whakatutukitanga rangahau, ngā rerenga ara mahi, ā, kia mārama "
"ake ai ki te mahere tauatanga me te tautoko i ētahi rōpū ake. \n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:62
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Prizes and/or medals are requested in order to enable analysis over "
"time of the causes and effects of recognition.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Ka tonoa ngā paraihe, mētara hoki/rānei kia taea ai te tātari i roto i te wā "
"i ngā pūtake me ngā pānga o te whakamana.\n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:67
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Please add any prizes, medals or awards you have received for your "
"research mahi.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Tāpirihia ngā paraihe, ngā mētara, ngā tohu rānei kua whiwhi koe mō ō mahi "
"rangahau."

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:72
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Information on professional bodies is useful for demonstrating "
"participation in the research community,\n"
"        including membership in organisations responsible for accreditation. "
"This space can also be used to record non-academic qualifications.<br/>\n"
"        Example Memberships include: Members of the Royal Society Te "
"Apārangi and New Zealand Association of Science Educators.<br/>\n"
"        Example Qualifications include: Chartered Practicing Accountant "
"(CPA) and Chartered Professional Engineer (CPEng), with the\n"
"        Organisation being the body that granted the qualification.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p>Ko ngā mōhiohio mō ngā rōpū ngaio, he whaitake mō te whakatauira i te "
"whai wāhitanga ki te hapori rangahau, tae atu ki te noho hei mema i roto i "
"ngā whakahaere mō te whakamanatanga. Ka taea hoki te whakamahi tēnei wāhi "
"hei tuhi i ngā tohu ehara i te mātauranga.</p><p>Ko ngā Mematanga tauira ko: "
"Ngā Mema o te Apārangi me te New Zealand Association of Science Educators.</"
"p><p>Ko ngā Tohu tauira ko: Kaikaute Whaitohu Mahi (CPA) me te Kaipūkaha "
"Ngaio Whaitohu (CPEng), ā, ko te Whakahaere ko te rōpū nā rātau i tuku te "
"tohu.</p>"

